gov.nist.javax.sip.parser
Interface MessageParserFactory

All Known Implementing Classes:
StringMsgParserFactory
public interface MessageParserFactory

Factory used to create message parser instances on behalf of the stack which are created when a new message comes from the network and is processed by the stack. This allows to plug other implementations of MessageParser than the ones provided by default with the jain sip stack
